Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是里見大人大駕光臨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願主的恩澤常伴你左右 永遠保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的神父容貌都很帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人賞心悅目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願主保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊那傢伙 還真是能裝親切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就不是神父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有份適合你的工作 來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼的 今早被里見這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒事…的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為來這裡的人都是因為身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你的某位親屬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是某位親屬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我不知道你是教會的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以坐在你的旁邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.09,0:01:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次來這裡 總覺得有些不安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不去排隊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是參加這個塗油的儀式來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…沒有資格那裡受祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是像你這樣的漂亮姐姐能來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡工作的我的青梅竹馬 也會非常高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願主原諒您 保佑您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇見了一位小小天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:24.82,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:24.82,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:29.29,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:29.29,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:35.60,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:35.60,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹著乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:42.07,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:42.07,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真偽 銘刻於心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.48,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.48,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈願待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:48.05,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:48.05,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛過 恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:51.55,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:51.55,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲傷最後化作溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:56.52,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:56.52,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:03:01.29,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:03:01.29,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍會尋覓明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:05.60,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:05.60,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:10.67,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:10.67,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之緣 最終轉化成奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.34,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.34,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:19.08,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:19.08,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撥開黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:22.91,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:22.91,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追尋你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:25.18,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:25.18,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.82,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.82,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總有一天 命運將會轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:33.49,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:33.49,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要讓眼淚白流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:38.13,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:38.13,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交織騷動的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.13,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.13,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}狂吠吧 交織的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊市街的人怎麼這麼混亂啊
